questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a financial transaction service is failing to roll back database changes during an exception. You find the following code snippet:

java
@Service
public class AuditService {
    @Transactional
    public void processAudit(Transaction tx) {
        try {
            saveRecord(tx);
        } catch (Exception e) {
            log.error("Audit failed", e);
            throw e;
        }
    }

    @Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)
    public void saveRecord(Transaction tx) {
        // JDBC Logic to insert record
    }
}
